<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-82-0823 </DOCNO><TEXT>Outlines the principles of automatic production control on the exampleof discontinuous coal mining technology employing shovel excavators,dumpers, crushers and belt conveyors. Principles of remote control andtime sequential switching on/off of five belt conveyors coupled in aseries line, as well as automatic control of one crushing plant are explained.The limits of such a system in mining practice are described. 5 refs.</TEXT></DOC>